# Publication Strategy

## Venue Tiers (CS/AI)
- Tier 1: NeurIPS, ICML, ICLR, CVPR, ACL, AAAI
- Tier 2: ECML, ICDM, PAKDD, MLSys, IEEE TPDS (journal)
- Always verify current CFP — deadlines/rates change yearly

## PhD Student Path
Workshop → Tier 2 → Tier 1 → Journal compilation

## Rebuttal (5-14 days window)
- Don't be defensive, acknowledge valid concerns
- Promise only what you can deliver
- Focus on fatal flaws, not nitpicks

## After Rejection
1. Rate each review: valid / partially valid / wrong
2. Fix legitimate issues
3. Resubmit to next venue (don't repeat without changes)

Typical path: NeurIPS reject → fix → ICML (3 months later)
